high_descs: Turn to your left cross the room and head to the stove
Pick the pan on the far left of the stove
Turn around to your right go straight to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in and out the pan then close the door
Turn around to right move forward then turn to your left face the last cabinet beside the fridge
Open the cabinet then put in the pan and close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the cold pan on the cabinet

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the counter, after that turn right and walk over to the oven.
Pick up the metal pan off of the back left burner of the stove.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the pan inside on the bottom shelf and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge, take the pan out, and close the fridge doors.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and start walking to the oven, turn left at the coffee machine and take a step forward and then turn left to face the counter.
Open the cabinet door below the counter and place the cold pan inside, then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan into a kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Cross the room to the door, turn right then right again to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove on the back burner.
Turn around and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the pan inside, close the door, open the door and pick up the pan.
Turn to face the lower white cabinet beside the refrigerator, to your right.
Open the cabinet door and place the pan inside the cabinet, close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan inside the cabinet beside the refrigerator.
